{"serial": "11047", "department_serial": 12, "code": "CL1094", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Applied literature of modern", "ch": "中文實務學"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Song,Yu-Wen", "Li,Xin-Lun"], "ch": ["宋玉雯", "李欣倫"]}, "credits": 2, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 4, "session": ["7", "8"]}, "loc": {"building": "C2", "room": "113"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 50, "department": {"ch": "中國文學系", "en": "Department of Chinese Literature"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "不使用", "en": "None"}, "assigned": 10, "selected": 24, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "本課程以介紹當今台灣文學相關產業，提供學生認識中文系畢業後就職的多樣性，因此邀請各領域的講者，除了分享個人職場經驗，也傳授各領域的實務經驗，包括企畫書寫作、採訪心法、編輯技巧和文學教育，並在期中、期末分別設計企畫書寫作和Podcast製作，讓同學在學習基本技巧後，進而練習小組實作。為了精進同學的能力，本課程也設計提案審查會議，邀請業師針對同學作品提供回饋，藉此讓同學認識文學相關產業之餘，也能活用各領域的基本技巧。", "en": "This course introduces the various industries related to contemporary Taiwanese literature, providing students with an understanding of the diverse career paths available to graduates of Chinese studies. To achieve this, we invite speakers from different fields to share their personal workplace experiences and practical knowledge, including proposal writing, interview techniques, editing skills, and literary education. Midway through and at the end of the course, students will work on proposal writing and podcast production projects, allowing them to practice group work after learning fundamental skills. To enhance students‘ abilities, the course also includes proposal review meetings where industry professionals provide feedback on students‘ work. This approach helps students gain insight into literature-related industries and effectively apply basic skills across various fields."}, "outline": {"ch": "週次日期內容講者\nweek19/12        課程說明\nweek29/19        從企畫、採訪、編輯到文學教育李欣倫\nweek39/26  企畫書寫作林奕圻\nweek410/3         撰寫企畫書李欣倫\nweek510/10國慶連假停課\nweek610/17企畫書相關蔡雨辰\nweek710/24企畫書講評會議林奕圻\nweek810/31      台北文學獎年金企畫申請案羅漪文\nweek911/7      作文補習班張馨潔\nweek1011/14高中老師分享卓育如\nweek1111/21全校運動會停課\nweek1211/28複合型的編輯經驗宋玉雯\nweek1312/5編輯出版相關劉子華\nweek1412/12人文學科的斜槓人生莊棨惟\nweek1512/19採訪報導房慧真\nweek1612/26採訪報導蔣亞妮\nweek171/2元旦連假\nweek181/9成果發表", "en": "weekdatecourse contentlecturer\n19/12Course Description\n29/19From Planning, Interviewing, Editing to Literary Education李欣倫\n39/26Proposal Writing林奕圻\n410/3Writing Proposals李欣倫\n510/10National Day Holiday, No Classes\n610/17Proposal-Related蔡雨辰\n710/24Proposal Review Meeting林奕圻\n810/31Taipei　Literary Award Fellowship Application羅漪文\n911/7Writing Tutoring張馨潔\n1011/14High School Teacher Sharing卓育如\n1111/21School Sports Day, No Classes\n1211/28Complex Editing Experience宋玉雯\n1312/5Editing and Publishing劉子華\n1412/12Multifaceted Careers in the Humanities莊棨惟\n1512/19Interview Reporting房慧真\n1612/26Interview Reporting蔣亞妮\n171/2New Year Holiday\n181/9Presentation of Results"}, "textbook": {"ch": "莎拉‧史坦‧葛林伯格《史丹佛設計學院：把好奇心化為點子的81個創意練習》，台北：大塊文化，2023", "en": "Sarah Stein Greenberg,”Creative Acts for Curious People: How to Think, Create, and Lead in Unconventional Ways”,2023"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "0", "en": "0"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "1. 課程心得及回饋：40％（挑選四週撰寫課程內容綱要和學習體會，每篇600字，期中11/15前繳交2篇，期末12/28 前繳交2篇，統一上傳至ee-class系統。）現場提問及回饋講師，一次發言可抵一次心得回饋，抵用以整學期一人／一次為限（但歡迎多提問發言）\n2. 企畫書：35％（書面企畫書＋提案簡報說明）\n3. 人物採訪 Podcast：35％（完整版20-30mis）\n4. 出缺勤及課堂參與：每堂課點名，缺課一次扣總成績3分。預先或事後請假，請email給助教宋俊磊", "en": "1.Course Reflections and Feedback: 40％ (Select four weeks to write summaries and reflections on the course content, with each entry being 600 words. Two entries are due by midterm, with a deadline of 11/15, and the remaining two entries are due by the end of the term, with a deadline of 12/28. All submissions should be uploaded to the EE-Class system.)\n2.Proposal: 35％ (Written proposal + presentation of the proposal.)\n3.Interview Podcast: 35％ (The complete version should be 20-30 minutes long.)"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "週三下午1:00-5:00", "en": "Wed 13:00-17:00"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "18", "en": "18"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "domain": {"ch": "應用中文", "en": "應用中文"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "文獻解讀", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試"]}, {"competencies": "邏輯思辨", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "作品/創作展演"]}, {"competencies": "語文表達", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "作品/創作展演"]}, {"competencies": "文學鑑賞", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["作業練習"]}, {"competencies": "人文素養與國際視野", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "作品/創作展演"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Interpreting classics", "rating": "(3)Medium", "assesments": ["Presentation/Oral Exam"]}, {"competencies": "Logical thinking", "rating": "(3)Medium", "assesments": ["Presentation/Oral Exam", "Products/Creative Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Language communication", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Presentation/Oral Exam", "Products/Creative Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Appreciation of literature", "rating": "(3)Medium", "assesments": ["Assignments"]}, {"competencies": "Humanistic and international outlook", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Presentation/Oral Exam", "Products/Creative Performance"]}]}, "assignCriteria": {"ch": ["系所:限中國文學系。年級:限一年級、二年級。", "系所:限中國文學系。"], "en": ["Department:Department of Chinese Literature only.Year:First Year、Second Year only.", "Department:Department of Chinese Literature only."]}, "preselecStu": 24, "stuGender": {"male": 4, "Female": 20}, "stuGrade": {"doctor": {}, "master": {}, "bachelor": {"4": 4, "3": 7, "2": 13}}, "stus": [{"serial": "1", "stunum": "10*******", "department": "中國文學系", "grade": "4", "class": "*", "priority": "1", "isRequired": false, "isPreselected": true, "isManuallySelected": false, "isCodeSelected": false}, {"serial": "2", "stunum": "11*******", "department": "中國文學系", "grade": "4", "class": "*", "priority": "1", "isRequired": false, "isPreselected": true, "isMa